<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\crt\libc\stdio\puts">puts</sample>
    <title> puts, putws</title>
    <volume>C 运行库函数</volume>
    <routine_idx> stio_idx.htm </routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>将字符串写入标准输出设备。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <func_name>puts</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>const char*</param_type>
                <param_name>string</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>指向要写入输出设备的字符串的指针</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <func_name>putws</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>const wchar_t*</param_type>
                <param_name>string</param_name>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
        <para>如果成功，返回非负值；否则，puts返回EOF，_putws返回WEOF。</para>
    </return>

    <remarks>
        <para>函数puts将string输出到标准输出设备，并将字符串结束符('\0')替换成换行符('\n')。</para>
    </remarks>

    <requirements>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>puts</routine_name>
            <headerfile>stdio.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>putws</routine_name>
            <headerfile>stdio.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
    </requirements>

    <example>
<pre>
//==========================================================================
// Copyright (c) 2000-2004,  Elastos, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.
//==========================================================================

/* puts.cpp: This program uses puts
 * to write a string to stdout.
 */

#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;

int main()
{
    puts(&quot;Hello world from puts!&quot;);

    return 0;
}
</pre>
    </example>
<result>
Hello world from puts!
</result>

    

